body_html:
Hi @sibyjackgrove,

Yes. This is a known issue.

I'm working on a fix so this doesn't happen again.
I'll just go patch it in the mean time.

The problem is that tf.keras.preprocessing and tf.keras.applications are now just wrappers for the keras_preprocessing and keras_applications packages.
